**BambiLand Styling Standards**

## Description
Styling standards for the BambiLand React Native application with pink-themed "bimbo/barbie" aesthetic.

## Applies to
**/*.{js,jsx,ts,tsx}

## Rules

### Color Palette
- Primary Pink: `#FF69B4` (Hot Pink) - Primary buttons, titles, key UI elements
- Secondary Pink: `#FFB6C1` (Light Pink) - Secondary text, backgrounds, accents
- Background Gradient: Linear gradient from `#FFF0F5` (Lavender Blush) to `#FFFFFF` (White)
- Accent Colors:
  - `#FF1493` (Deep Pink) - Important actions, highlights
  - `#FFC0CB` (Pink) - Subtle backgrounds, dividers
  - `#FFFFFF` (White) - Card backgrounds, text on dark backgrounds
  - `#000000` (Black) - Sparingly for text
  - `#4CAF50` (Green) - Success states
  - `#FF5252` (Red) - Error states
  - `#FFC107` (Amber) - Warning states

### Typography
- Title Font:
  - iOS: `Noteworthy-Bold` with italic styling
  - Android: `Cursive` with italic styling
  - Sizes: 24dp–30dp (main titles), 18dp–22dp (section titles)
  - Color: `#FF69B4` (Hot Pink)
  - Text Shadow: Subtle pink glow (`rgba(255, 105, 180, 0.3)`)
  - Letter Spacing: 0.5px
- Body Font:
  - iOS: System font
  - Android: `Roboto`
  - Sizes: 14dp–16dp (primary text), 12dp (secondary text)
  - Color: `#FFB6C1` (Light Pink), `#FF69B4` for emphasis
  - Line Height: 1.5× font size

### UI Elements
- Buttons:
  - Primary Button: 48dp height, 24dp corner radius, 24dp horizontal padding
  - Secondary Button: 44dp height, 1dp border, 22dp corner radius
  - Icon Button: 40dp × 40dp, minimum 44dp × 44dp touch target
- Cards:
  - Standard Card: 16dp padding, 16dp corner radius, 2dp shadow
  - Featured Card: 280dp × 180dp, 16dp corner radius
  - Post Card: Screen width - 32dp, 16dp padding, 16dp corner radius
- Input Fields:
  - Text Input: 48dp height, 8dp corner radius, 16dp padding
  - Text Area: 120dp min height, 8dp corner radius, 16dp padding
  - Search Input: 40dp height, 20dp corner radius, 16dp padding

### Animation Language
- Transitions: Spring animation (tension: 40, friction: 8), 300ms duration
- Feedback: Scale 0.95×–1.05× on press
- Loading: Pink pulsing or spinning gradient circles
- Page Transitions: Slide and fade (300ms)
